ISLAMABAD, Apr 11 (APP): Vice President Pakistan Tehreek-e-Insaf (PTI) Shah Mehmood Qureshi on Monday announced en masse resignation from the National Assembly.
Speaking on a point of order, he said that they have decided not to be part of elections of leader of house and were going to tender their resignation.
